{"tid":2048842,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"揚州男子網上被騙　向「網警」求助   豈料警察...都是假的...","createTime":"2020-06-03T05:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T11:59:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"cc44000799c575bcbd41744775bdeb0405a5bab8","tid":2048842,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:28:57.000Z","msg":"【揚州男子網上被騙　向「網警」求助】<br />\n【豈料警察...都是假的...】<br />\n<br />\n揚州一名男子打工時，在網上被騙了約兩萬多元。於是他在網上報警，希望網警能為他討回公道。<br />\n<br />\n豈料報警後，連網警也是假的！對方要求男子將所有資金，轉移到同一個賬戶，進行安全處理。男子不慎將所有錢轉進去後，發現情況可疑，於是再次報警。<br />\n<br />\n警方經過調查後，發現全國有多宗類似案件，資金都被轉到海南，最終在當地搗破一個詐騙集團。目前相關涉案人員，已被採取強制措施。<br />\n<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n#假網警<br />\n#詐騙集團<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2561109724033498/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F2561109724033498%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=9MYRmPDtC2YjWedq%2F%2FxxgYL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=0dd76212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2561109724033498/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"724b06c273d7d13a7f1093d256a82f251e8f32b2","tid":2048842,"uid":354367,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"痴撚書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ce4b69efb02e343db600b6057e5f43765e45d0","tid":2048842,"uid":71237,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"佢點搵網警先？"},{"pid":"694684e7bae926a6cb2d78242dd480c78b102620","tid":2048842,"uid":20658,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"19ce4b69efb02e343db600b6057e5f43765e45d0","tid":2048842,"uid":71237,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"佢點搵網警先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:37:01.000Z","msg":"百度網警囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0a72273bb3230ed46a3ee51cfa3606b70cb93d","tid":